flowchart TD
  A[Trigger: Monthly sales data update and new product launch announcements.]
  A --> N1[Stream: DDM/Crawlers - Ingest monthly sales data]
  N1 --> N2[Cortex: Cortex Auto Forecast - Generate global sales forecast]
  N2 --> N3[Cortex: RCA Service - Integrate market trends]
  N3 --> N4[Cortex: AutoML - Forecast initial demand for new products]
  N4 --> N5{PB: CWB Lifecycle - Adopt global sales forecast scenario}
  N5 -->|Primary| N6[PB: Remote Functions - Adjust forecast methods based on error analysis]
  N6 --> Z1[Outcome: Improved revenue capture, better availability, faster adaptation to demand shifts, and reduced working capital tied to forecast errors.]
  N5 -->|Significant demand deviation detected| B1[Trigger reforecasting]
  B1 --> O1[Outcome: Updated forecast]
  O1 --> End[End]
  N5 -->|High forecast error| B2[Review and adjust forecast methods]
  B2 --> O2[Outcome: Improved forecast accuracy]
  O2 --> End[End]
  N5 -->|Insufficient market data| B3[Delay decision until more data available]
  B3 --> O3[Outcome: Hold off on forecast adoption]
  O3 --> End[End]
  Z1 --> End[End]